==Bringing Anti-Santa the tears==
* '''Anti-Santa:''' Great work, I know you'd have it in you! Give me a moment to purify these tears and then we can continue.
* {{tbox|Anti-Santa takes the vial and absorbs a sorrowful essence from the liquid within.}}
* '''Anti-Santa:''' I've purified the tears into this sorrowful solution, all you have to do is pour it into the machine over there!
* {{tact|end}}

===Using the vial of sorrow on the machine===
* {{tbox|You pour the purified tears into the machine...}}
* {{tbox|...the blizzard lets out a howl of sorrow...}}
* {{tbox|...hideous creatures emerge from the frost!}}
* {{qact|Frosty spiders and frosty snakelings appear around the machine.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Anti-Santa===
* '''Anti-Santa:''' Finally, my army of sorrow brought to life!
* '''Player:''' These creatures, they're made from the tears I collected?
* '''Anti-Santa:''' Precisely! The sadness harvested from those tears has manifested into beings of pure sorrow, nothing will be able to stop them!
* '''Player:''' What are you planning to do with them?
* '''Anti-Santa:''' I shall prepare them for battle, and when the time is right, we shall storm the White Knights' Castle!
* '''Anti-Santa:''' You have proven your inner malevolence and earned this reward.
* {{tact|end}}

